overview:
Jomie is a professional design services provider and consultant for brands, print design and design items. We provide designs, advising services and production of good visuals items with quality, a range of other products that are manufactured for our customers’. Jomie leverages art, design and technology to advance the business process.

Jomie is focusing, creating or/and consulting in designs, branding and communication design listed in the design industry, high quality prints and visuals with color management, design luxury & quality packaging mockups & boxes, shopping bags, design products, plastic advertising - companies signs, gifts, home and office decor design items, successful marketing materials and concepts for well known companies or individuals. Jomie also helps to design your showroom suitable for your new launch products.
